name: Objktape#001
description:
Objktape#001 is a mixtape by Music Producer and DJ Re-Surge. His first compilation have several authorial instrumentals and 
poems by poets such as: Miró da Muribeca, Leonardo Bastião, Carlos Drummond de Andrade, Fernando Pessoa and others.

A somewhat melancholy nftape with a strong Brazilian spice.


All songs produced by @re_surgee
